                            <comment id="13007066" author="jbellis" created="Tue, 15 Mar 2011 18:22:16 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Patch to remove use of maximumpoolsize in favor of core size + timing out core threads.  Also adds memtable_flush_queue_size configuration directive, defaulting to 4.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13007102" author="brandon.williams" created="Tue, 15 Mar 2011 19:04:08 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;+1, increased flush queue size is enough to prevent blocking writes at all with stress and an index.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
